	This file describes files that should be pulled into a ZIP file to be sent
	out for localizing.  Each file descriptor should be relative to the root of the
	picnik repository.  Use * and ? as wildcards if you want.

	This file is read in by zip_loc_sources.py to produce a loc_sources.zip file.
-->
